{"tid":1873160,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"攞免費口罩嘅70歲陳婆婆鬧爆林鄭無能，並即場怒刪與林鄭的珍藏合照！","createTime":"2020-02-10T13:06:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T20:21:35.000Z","uid":1886,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"cbb1398344bc45bbee15a02b5706247ec6764bab","tid":1873160,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T13:06:38.000Z","msg":"政府抗疫無能，全城一罩難求，今日有比政府更貼地、更積極的私人公司，一起解市民所憂加入抗疫行列，在高官口中「採購困難」的環境下，仍能為港人輸入口罩應急，免費派發口罩逾萬個。70歲的陳婆婆今日連早餐也不吃，為了口罩便先到大角嘴排隊搶免費口罩，「我覺得呢個政府不知所謂， 警察就有口罩，護士唔夠口罩，市民冇口罩，你話呢個政府係咪值得，點講，對呢個政府真係好反感」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200210/KWXSKO6HDLAXZH2FXJ6K7NBVXE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200210%2FKWXSKO6HDLAXZH2FXJ6K7NBVXE%2F&d=u5wkwi0qRaq%2FdbVqa5yG4WAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=8366d4b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200210%2FKWXSKO6HDLAXZH2FXJ6K7NBVXE%2F&h=6696c3d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200210/KWXSKO6HDLAXZH2FXJ6K7NBVXE/</a>"},{"pid":"a5f0baf79f2008522ada7c0f5c842f42a429235a","tid":1873160,"uid":1886,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T13:07:21.000Z","msg":"陳婆婆指自己是長期病患者，所以較保護自己，出街除了戴口罩外，更會戴上太陽眼鏡及穿上便利雨衣，盡可能減低病毒感染的機會，「我覺得林鄭真係要反省，我哋一把年紀仲要為口罩排隊」，認為口罩應該由林鄭政府派給市民 。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200210/large/1581322395_3492.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200210%2Flarge%2F1581322395_3492.jpg&h=0908fed2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳婆婆原本是林鄭的忠實擁躉，當年與林鄭的合照一直珍藏至今，「 我期望佢係一位好特首，點知佢比任何一位特首更差，對佢非常失望」，「佢哋一直隱瞞（疫情），中央隱瞞，佢哋又隱瞞，唔公佈先搞到咁嘅田地」，語畢，隨即在一眾傳媒面前，將該張與林鄭的合照從手機中刪除。"},{"pid":"0922d53030124f9dc0d5d7115bc417ab0d610a94","tid":1873160,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T13:08:45.000Z","msg":"陳婆婆原本是林鄭的忠實擁躉，當年與林鄭的合照一直珍藏至今。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200210/large/1581320544_5a89.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200210%2Flarge%2F1581320544_5a89.jpg&h=3ba729c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0e1142ca25d595928ebbbb1b69064ac3b1be5cdc","tid":1873160,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T13:10:05.000Z","msg":"遊行唔到，集會唔到。至少要Home Office 抗爭<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1873140\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1873140</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6e0fe2215a7e63fa04cf7860330dfb7c697696e3","tid":1873160,"uid":258696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T13:11:40.000Z","msg":"人一藍 <br />\n腦便殘<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4225fe1757be4367d13e44e8edf57dec67f3c69","tid":1873160,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T13:41:18.000Z","msg":"籃轉黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e9271e48c4b5a4aa98beb7abfd37a84ae3d76a6","tid":1873160,"uid":108016,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T13:41:56.000Z","msg":"廢老藍屍"},{"pid":"491612b996dbd4ae5f894f7d56055163557f2877","tid":1873160,"uid":70487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T13:42:45.000Z","msg":"笑𠹌咗"},{"pid":"3be02de262239a5b098b9ecb9411345bfb635fb3","tid":1873160,"uid":15880,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T13:43:02.000Z","msg":"林鄭: 正義係我個邊, 市民唔好口罩政治化, 否則我搵警察殺你全家"},{"pid":"ac30467fff16887ff1f28514408d16e3f9037a36","tid":1873160,"uid":175346,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T13:44:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce969cd6c0e8c9f4d833f9268568d34a24d91a85","tid":1873160,"uid":248290,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T13:44:51.000Z","msg":"藍轉黃<img src=\"/assets